<p>
I had a chat with <a href="http://twitter.com/kevsmith" target="_blank">Kevin Smith</a> to talk about <a href="http://www.basho.com/" target="_blank">basho</a>, how <a href="http://wiki.basho.com/display/RIAK/Riak" target="_blank">riak</a> works, and what the <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/CAP_theorem" target="_blank">CAP theorem</a> is.
