<div class="podcast_episode_notes">
<p>
I had a chat with <a href="http://blip.tv/about/jared/" target="_blank">Jared Klett</a> to talk about <a href="http://blip.tv//" target="_blank">blip.tv</a>, dealing with 200 servers, and managing 1.4 Petabytes.
